title: Spiced carrot cake with walnuts
ingredients: ['6 eggs', '2 pinches ground cinnamon', '1 pinch ground nutmeg', '1 pinch ground cardamom (optional)', 'seeds of 1/2 vanilla pod', '150g caster sugar', '200ml vegetable oil', '350g plain flour', '1 teaspoon baking powder', '1 pinch salt', '250ml milk', '110g chopped walnuts', '130g grated carrots']
